he head of consumer retail but only one person (maybe two) gets to be it. A=
t a hedge fund with a dozen analysts, probably each analyst will have her o=
wn fairly large coverage universe. If you=E2=80=99re the analyst covering c=
onsumer retail companies, then you are also the =E2=80=9Chead of consumer r=
etail.=E2=80=9D Who else could it be? You are the head of a team of one, bu=
t that=E2=80=99s a pretty common experience in the financial industry.

