=E2=80=9CNo one else in the MEV ecosystem was doing both of those things at=
 once that we know of,=E2=80=9D he added. =E2=80=9CThey did more than just =
play by both the codified and pinky promise rules of MEV extraction.=E2=80=
=9D
=E2=80=9CIt's not some kind of robin hood story as they didn't return the m=
oney to people MEVers extracted it from,=E2=80=9D pseudonymous researcher B=
anteg said.

Well, no, they=E2=80=99re not going to=C2=A0return=C2=A0the money.

