; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">would=
 absolutely have used</a> the word =E2=80=9Cblockchain.=E2=80=9D In 2024 it=
 does not. I suppose that is some sort of progress.</p>
